<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Leave Request Not Approved</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #0A0A0A;
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E5E5;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #171717;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 0;
        }
        .page-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #171717;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .rejected-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #EF4444;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            padding: 4px 14px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            vertical-align: middle;
            margin-left: 10px;
        }
        .leave-info {
            background-color: #F5F5F5;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E5E5;
        }
        .info-row:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
            padding-bottom: 0;
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .info-label {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #737373;
        }
        .info-value {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #171717;
        }
        .reason-section {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .reason-section h3 {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #171717;
        }
        .reason-text {
            background-color: #FEF2F2;
            border: 1px solid #FECACA;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            color: #7F1D1D;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        .next-steps {
            background-color: #F5F5F5;
            padding: 16px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #525252;
        }
        .next-steps ul {
            margin: 8px 0 0 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .next-steps li {
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            border-top: 1px solid #E5E5E5;
            color: #737373;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">Employee Management System</div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h1 class="page-title">
                Leave Request
                <span class="rejected-badge">Not Approved</span>
            </h1>

            <p>Dear {{employeeName}},</p>

            <p>We regret to inform you that your leave request has not been approved by <strong>{{approverName}}</strong>. Please review the details below:</p>

            <div class="leave-info">
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Leave Type:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{leaveType}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">From:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{fromDate}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">To:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{toDate}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Total Duration:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{days}} day(s)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Reviewed By:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{approverName}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="reason-section">
                <h3>Reason for Rejection:</h3>
                <div class="reason-text">{{reason}}</div>
            </div>

            <div class="next-steps">
                <strong>What you can do next:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>Speak directly with your manager to discuss the decision</li>
                    <li>Submit a revised leave request for alternative dates if applicable</li>
                    <li>Contact HR if you believe this decision needs to be reviewed</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <p>We understand this may be disappointing. Please feel free to reach out to your manager or HR for further clarification.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message from the Employee Management System.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
